Hotkeys on Microsoft Word

***************************

(Windows)

Switch Programs:
Alt+Tab

Create a new document:
Ctrl+N

Open a document:
Ctrl+O

Save the document:
Ctrl+S

Print the document:
Ctrl+P

Close the document:
Ctrl+W

Select all text:
Ctrl+A

Double Space:
Ctrl+2

Copy text:
Ctrl+C

Paste text:
Ctrl+V

Cut text:
Ctrl+X

Copy Formatting:
Ctrl+Shift+C

Paste Formatting:
Ctrl+Shift+V

Highlight text:
Shift-Left or Shift-Right (Same on Mac)

Bold formatting:
Ctrl+B

Italics formatting:
Ctrl+I

Underline text:
Ctrl+U

Page Break:
Ctrl+Enter

Decrease the font size by 1 point:
Ctrl+Left bracket ([)

Increase the font size by 1 point:
Ctrl+Right bracket (])

Center text:
Ctrl+E

Align the text to the left:
Ctrl+L

Align the text to the right:
Ctrl+R

Undo the previous action:
Ctrl+Z

Redo the previous action, if possible:
Ctrl+Y

Repeat last action performed:
F4  ** On Mac - Command+Y

Split the document window and remove split:
Ctrl+Alt+S

Find text:
Ctrl+F

Spell Checker:
F7 ** On Mac - Command+Option+L
